cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SY, cs.AR 

This paper deals with software diversity and crash reporting, which are topics related to computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also presents adaptations to existing compiler tools, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the mitigation of code injection and code reuse attacks, which is related to computer architecture (cs.AR).
